 {td}**Multi-Site / Multi-Zone Management**{/td}
 {td}SR-8.1 and SR-8.2 invalidated per review R6 — close GMS-85 and GMS-86 as Invalid; capture architectural intent as a design note outside the requirements baseline{/td}
 {td}Vremere Adrian{/td}
